  {
    "content_id": 798039,
    "reference_id": 20326,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>恨惡：神恨惡破裂的約（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:3\">1:3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:15\">何9:15</a>）。這是合宜的，因為神與人的關係的特徵就是信實，祂對以色列的期望也不例外（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6\">出34:6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">申7:9</a>）。</p></li><li><p>休妻（字面意思是<em>打發走</em>）意指驅逐婚姻伴侶。瑪拉基希望糾正對休妻律法的濫用（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:1-Deut24:4\">申24:1–4</a>）。</p></li><li><p>以強暴待妻：強暴意味著暴力或不當的行為。休妻是一種暴力且殘酷的社會罪行。休妻是對妻子、也是對婚姻盟約的背叛。它使人心碎、破壞關係、破壞家庭的完整性、損害孩子的福祉，使未來岌岌可危。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:16",
          "end_ref": "39002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798041,
    "reference_id": 20328,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>瑪拉基的聽眾質疑神的公義，以此煩瑣耶和華。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:17",
          "end_ref": "39002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798040,
    "reference_id": 20327,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:17–3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002017-39003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>瑪拉基的第四段信息涉及神的公義與人的公義之間的差異（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:17\">2:17</a>）。如果瑪拉基書是一部法庭劇，那麼第四段信息就是對猶大的正式起訴。瑪拉基指控盡職但無心的宗教行為（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:14\">3:14</a>），這與神的公義相悖；他呼籲誠實和真正的社會關懷。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:17",
          "end_ref": "39003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798055,
    "reference_id": 20342,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>我的使者（希伯來文mal’aki）：這是瑪拉基的名字的文字遊戲。使者指的可能是天使或作為神的使者的人。耶穌引用這段經文來說明施洗約翰的身份（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:10\">太11:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:2\">可1:2</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:27\">路7:27</a>）。</p></li><li><p>瑪拉基的聽眾可能會認為立約的使者是一位屬天的存在（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20-Exod23:23\">出23:20–23</a>）。基督教會則認為耶穌基督就是新的約的使者。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:1",
          "end_ref": "39003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798056,
    "reference_id": 20343,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>火：百姓邪惡的渣滓必須被神的試煉和刑罰的火燒盡（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:25\">賽1:25</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:29\">耶6:29</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:22\">結22:22</a>）。</p></li><li><p>鹼：從植物中提煉的鹼性的清潔劑（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:22\">耶2:22</a>）。火和鹼象徵了火燒的試煉和漂洗的潔凈，<span>藉此恢復以色列對耶和華的約的忠實</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:2",
          "end_ref": "39003002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798057,
    "reference_id": 20344,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>速速作見證暗示了這是一場法律訴訟，其中神既是檢察官（起訴者），又是關鍵證人（提供證據者），針對被擄後的猶大。</p></li><li><p>行邪術的為了個人利益而從事巫術、邪術或占卜。</p></li><li><p>即將到來的神的審判之日會洗淨罪孽深重的猶大人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:3\">3:3</a>）或毀滅他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1-Mal4:2\">4:1–2</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:5",
          "end_ref": "39003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798058,
    "reference_id": 20345,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:6–12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003006-39003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>瑪拉基的第五段信息回應了第一段信息（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:2-Mal1:5\">1:2–5</a>），強調神忠於祂的應許。祂呼籲以色列在敬拜中<span>也要保持相同</span>的信實，尤其是在他們的什一奉獻和供物上。如果瑪拉基書是一場法庭劇，那麼第五段信息就是法官的裁決。真正的信息是悔改——神期望祂的百姓進行誠實和真摯的敬拜，而什一奉獻就是其象徵。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:6",
          "end_ref": "39003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798059,
    "reference_id": 20346,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在盟約關係的語境中，轉向表達出以色列或神所忠於的對象改變。這個詞通常被理解為悔改，即完全轉向神或完全重新歸向耶和華。這個使役動詞傳達了緊迫性，要求聽眾立即回應。對不誠實敬拜的指控，是在第二次辯論中的類似指控的基礎上提出的（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6-Mal1:14\">1:6–14</a>），就像神應許「打開天上的窗戶」（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">3:10</a>）證實了祂作為「大君王」的能力（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:14\">1:14</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:7",
          "end_ref": "39003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798060,
    "reference_id": 20347,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003008-39003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>瑪拉基呼籲猶大全面更新他們對耶和華的奉獻的實踐。</p></li><li><p>十分之一——即土地產物的十分之一——是必須的奉獻（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:6\">申12:6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:11\">11</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:17\">17</a>）。供物是對耶和華或祂的聖所額外的禮物或奉獻，包括農產品、物品（如建築材料或衣物）或個人貴重財物（如金、銀或寶石）。</p></li><li><p>猶大最近的經歷是因為神的詛咒（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:20\">申28:20</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:27\">27</a>）。因此，瑪拉基急迫呼籲群體悔改、轉向耶和華，並履行盟約的要求。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:8",
          "end_ref": "39003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798046,
    "reference_id": 20333,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以此試試我！<span>這神聖的邀請給予歸回的群體一個機會，來證明神對其盟約應許的信實</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:10",
          "end_ref": "39003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798047,
    "reference_id": 20334,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>萬國必稱你們為有福的：豐富的農產品將再次向世界顯明耶和華對以色列的喜悅。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:12",
          "end_ref": "39003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798049,
    "reference_id": 20336,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你們用話頂撞我：人們指責神偏袒作惡者，並公然質疑祂的公義（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:17\">2:17</a>），但耶和華喜愛公義（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:16\">詩9:16</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:28\">37:28</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:13",
          "end_ref": "39003013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798048,
    "reference_id": 20335,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:13–4:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003013-39004003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>瑪拉基最後的信息包含兩段不同但相關的講論，第一段強調對耶和華的事奉（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:13-Mal3:18\">3:13–18</a>），第二段對比惡人和義人的命運（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1-Mal4:3\">4:1–3</a>）。每段講論都以使者公式結束（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"20320\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">1:8的研讀註釋</span>）。先知重申第四段信息的主題（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:1-Mal3:5\">3:1–5</a>），強調神期望誠實和忠誠的敬拜，因為耶和華審判的日子即將來臨。如果瑪拉基書是一場法庭劇，這最後的爭論就是審判。雖然邪惡似乎勝過公義，且神似乎<span>未及時在群體中審判罪惡</span>，但即將到來的耶和華的日子將證明神的公義，因為惡人將在神的審判之火中與義人分開。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:13",
          "end_ref": "39004003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 4:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 20320,
          "content_id": 798033,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "瑪拉基書 1:8",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798050,
    "reference_id": 20337,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>有甚麼益處呢？人們認為正義的行為會帶來物質上的祝福（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:68\">申28章</a>）。</p></li><li><p>苦苦齋戒：這指的是悲傷地遊行或穿著喪服行走以示悔改，彷彿這樣的行為本身就是正義的（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:1-Matt6:18\">太6:1–18</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:14",
          "end_ref": "39003014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798051,
    "reference_id": 20338,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>稱狂傲的人為有福是在褻瀆神的公義（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:13\">3:13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:15",
          "end_ref": "39003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798053,
    "reference_id": 20340,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>紀念冊——一種波斯傳統——是一份名錄，並記錄了與那些人的相關事件。我們不知道有多少人簽署了這份卷冊。</p></li><li><p>敬畏耶和華的人是指那些忠於<span>耶和華為神、遵行神的命令、行為與敬拜公義的人</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:16",
          "end_ref": "39003016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798052,
    "reference_id": 20339,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:16–18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003016-39003018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>先知在此充當記錄者，報告聽眾對他最後信息的反應，以及神對那些敬畏耶和華之人的討論的回應。</span>雖然神聽了他們的討論（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:16\">3:16</a>），但沒有證據表明瑪拉基的信息對大多數聽眾產生了任何實質性的改變。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:16",
          "end_ref": "39003018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798054,
    "reference_id": 20341,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>特特歸我：以色列作為神的子民擁有特殊的地位，他們是神私人的產業。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:17",
          "end_ref": "39003017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798061,
    "reference_id": 20348,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 4:1–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39004001-39004003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這段信息不再以辯論的形式呈現，而是直接警告人們，悔改是對耶和華的信息唯一正確的回應，因為神的審判是無法逃避的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39004001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 4:1",
          "end_ref": "39004003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 4:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798062,
    "reference_id": 20349,
    "title": "瑪拉基書 4:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39004002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>公義的日頭這個稱呼的來源，可能是古代近東圖像中普遍出現的有翼太陽圓盤。在這裡，它可能是彌賽亞的稱號，或是<span>象徵一個新的公義時代的比喻性描述</span>。在這個時代中，神將除去罪的咒詛。以色列的屬靈復興或醫治將建立在神潔淨百姓並赦免他們的罪的基礎上（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:8\">耶33:6–8</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:14-Jer8:15\">耶8:14–15</a>）。這將源自於集體的認罪並回轉歸向神（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:7\">瑪3:7</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:19-Jer14:20\">耶14:19–20</a>）。</p></li><li><p>在他翼下（和合本譯為：光線）：展開的翅膀是神保護和拯救的象徵（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:4\">出19:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:10-Deut32:11\">申32:10–11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8\">詩17:8</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:10\">18:10</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
